I'm glad you asked. I think this is a hold-over from when directories were referred to as "packages". It got a bit confusing when "package" was used to describe project structure *and* units of sharable Dart code, as seen in the pubspec.yaml file. IIRC the former was dropped a few years ago. I'd forgotten about that.

I'll re-open this issue since it does seem like a real problem.

@pq @devoncarew Do you have any further insights?
